ywhere, I don't - I don't remember - going visit - yes, I - yes, I - I remember - as long as I can - I can remember, going over - from Pendeen to Leedstown, where - to see some - fellow that my father had been working with in - South Africa. Yes. Called -
 Owtie. He'd got a son - living at Trewellard now who was apparently his friend. They're all dead - except him. Yes. Oaty I think. Yes, Leedstown, yes.
